The significance of Jesus Christ
The Gospel Book of Jesus the Messiah, son of David, son of Abraham:
Ibrahim ولد إسحاق. And Isaac ولد يعقوب. And Jacob ولد يهوذا and his brothers.
And Judah was born to Serah and Zerah from Tamar. And Serah was born to Eshton. And Eshton was born to Aram.
And Aram had two brothers, Aminadab, and Aminadab had Nahshon, and Nahshon had Salmon.
Salmon was born of Rahab. And Boaz was born of Edom. And Edom was born of Esheba.
Wasa bint Dawud the king. And David the king was the son of Solomon from Bathsheba.
And Solomon was born to Reubem. And Reubem was born to Nahor. And Nahor was born to Asa.
And Joshua, the son of Yeoshua. And Yeoshua, the son of Yoram. And Yoram, the son of Eliashama.
And عزيا comforted Yoatham. And Yoatham was the son of Aziah. And Aziah was the son of Haggai.
And Josiah was born of Memnon. And Memnon was born of Amun. And Amun was born of Joshua.
Joshua and his relatives were born in Babylon and among its people.
And after the captivity of Babylon, Kennya, son of Sheltaiiel, was born. And Sheltaiiel was born of Zerbabel.
Zarababel was born of Ahab. And Ahab was born of Igal. And Igal was born of Azor.
And Azaz son of Sadduq. And Sadduq son of Akheem. And Akheem son of Elyud.
