That news spread throughout that land. Healing for the blind.
As Jesus was passing by, two blind men cried out and said, “Lord, have mercy on us, you son of David!”
And when he came to the house, the two blind men approached him, and Jesus said to them, “Do you believe that I am able to do this?” They said to him, “Yes, Lord!”
And then he touched their eyes and said, “According to your faith, let it be.”
Their eyes opened. Jesus rebuked them, saying, “Behold, you know nothing!”
But they went out and spread it throughout all the land. A cure for the mute.
